data.description: Check out this great home with canal water view. 2500 square feet, work shop, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths. A private neighborhood boat launch and plenty of boat parking and RV parking. Voluntary HOA for $35 per year! This neighborhood has underground utilities. This home features a large family room with cathedral ceilings and a large stacked stone fireplace with a custom mantle. This home has storage galore plus two safes! Large laundry room with additional sink. Spacious kitchen with stainless appliances. Workshop in the back yard that is large enough to finish off as a detached garage. Large back yard, perfect for a pool or garden. Windows 2020, HVAC 2019 and Seller to put new roof on at closing! Front extra room with it's own entrance that you can easily run your business out of or have a work from home office. Gulf Breeze Schools! Make your appointment today!
